T* () Tj
T* (To: Hatch) Tj
T* (RE: Account ACC-123 ∑ DOS 2024-05-05) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Dear Billing Department,) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (I am writing to formally dispute charges totaling $1,670.00 on the above-referenced account. This dispute is) Tj
T* (submitted pursuant to 45 CFR ß 149.620, which establishes the federal patient-provider dispute resolution) Tj
T* (process. An independent audit of the itemized statement has identified coding and billing errors that require) Tj
T* (correction.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The following line items are disputed:) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. CPT 29877 ó Arthroscopy, knee, surgical; debridement/shaving of articular cartilage ó $875.00. This) Tj
T* (procedure code appears to have been billed in violation of National Correct Coding Initiative \(NCCI\) edits.) Tj
T* (Per the NCCI Policy Manual, Chapter 4, CPT 29877 is frequently bundled with other arthroscopic) Tj
T* (procedures performed during the same operative session and may not be separately billable without) Tj
T* (appropriate documentation and modifier usage. No such modifier or supporting documentation has been) Tj
T* (provided.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. Patient Responsibility Balance ó $795.00. This balance includes amounts attributable to the improperly) Tj
T* (unbundled CPT 29877 charge described above. Under the No Surprises Act, 45 CFR ß 149.410 and ß) Tj
T* (2799B-1, patients may not be balance-billed for amounts stemming from improper coding, lack of prior) Tj
T* (authorization, or other provider billing errors. The patient responsibility must be recalculated after correction) Tj
T* (of the underlying coding error.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (To ensure transparency and auditability, the original itemized statement has been cryptographically hashed) Tj
T* (\(SHA-256: 4e14685c57214ae5011eb88530b8318f089885869dce9c5f395d7125951775db\) and anchored on) Tj
T* (the 0G Chain decentralized ledger. This immutable record preserves the integrity of the disputed bill for) Tj
T* (regulatory review.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (I respectfully request that you provide a corrected, compliant itemized statement within thirty \(30\) calendar) Tj
T* (days of receipt of this letter, along with written explanation of all adjustments made. If you believe the) Tj
T* (original charges are correct, please provide the operative report, modifier justification, and NCCI edit) Tj
T* (override documentation to support separate billing of CPT 29877.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter. I look forward to an amicable resolution in accordance) Tj
T* (with applicable federal regulations.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Sincerely,) Tj
T* (Justin) Tj
